<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/221> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #221" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Demanded redress from the Aequi for invading Latin territory contrary to the treaty (Liv. 3.25.6-9; cf. Dion. Hal. 10.22.4-6). On Volumnius, see Lübker no. 2, and on Postumius, no. 16." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/220> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #220" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Possibly the same as Dion. Hal. reports in 466 (9.60.3-68; see RE s. v. \"Fabius\" no. 165)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/197> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #197" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "ILS 9338, 2 ([-Postu]mius A. f. P. n. Albus [- - -]); coopted this year. See 439, note 4; Degrassi 91; Lübker nos. 17 and 16, respectively." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/196> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #196" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "ILS 9338, 2 ([-Postu]mius A. f. P. n. Albus [- - -]); coopted this year. See 439, note 4; Degrassi 91; Lübker nos. 17 and 16, respectively." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/180> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #180" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 3.4.1; Diod. 11.78.1; Fast. Cap. (P.'s name entire except Regill[ens.]); Dion. Hal. 9.62.1; Chr. 354 (Religiense et Medullino III); Cassiod.; Degrassi 24f., 91, 360f. The Consuls carried on separate operations against the Aequi, Furius in Hernican territory (Liv. 3.4.7-5.13; Dion. Hal. 9.62.2-66.4). On Postumius, see Lübker, no. 16." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/108> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #108" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Appointed to dedicate the temple of Castor (Liv. 2.42.5; cf. Iordan, Topogr. 1.2.370). See Lübker, no. 16 or 17." .
